---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
import { GAME_NAME, CURRENT_VERSION } from '../data/site';

const pageSourceIds = ['DB-API-001'];
---

<ContentLayout
  title="Beginner Guide"
  description="Beginner guide for Demon Born Roblox — official scope, player routes, and controls overview."
  canonicalUrl="/beginner-guide/"
  breadcrumb={[{ label: 'Beginner Guide', url: '/beginner-guide/' }]}
  evidenceNotes="Official confirmed limited — broad facts verified; detailed steps require hands-on testing"
  sourceIds={pageSourceIds}
>
  <h1>{GAME_NAME} Beginner Guide</h1>

  <p class="page-lead">
    Getting started with {GAME_NAME} on Roblox — official facts only.
    Detailed walkthrough steps require hands-on testing and are not yet published.
  </p>

  <div class="info-note">
    <strong>Version:</strong> {CURRENT_VERSION}.
    This page contains only officially confirmed facts. Detailed quest steps,
    level progression, and combat mechanics require hands-on testing.
  </div>

  <h2>What the official description says</h2>
  <p>
    The Roblox game description for <em>[WORLD CUP BETA] Demon Born</em> (source: <code>DB-API-001</code>)
    establishes the following:
  </p>

  <div class="info-block">
    <strong>Genre:</strong> Action RPG, RPG<br />
    <strong>Setting:</strong> Open world with mysteries and challenging quests<br />
    <strong>Theme:</strong> Demons<br />
    <strong>Player count:</strong> 1 (at time of retrieval — <code>DB-API-001</code>; may change)
  </div>

  <h2>The two player routes</h2>
  <p>
    The official description explicitly offers two player routes:
  </p>
  <div class="table-wrapper">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Route</th>
          <th>Official wording</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Slayer route</td>
          <td>Become a slayer — fight demons</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Demon route</td>
          <td>Embrace the dark side and fight to destroy humanity</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <p>
    The specific differences between these routes (stat allocations, abilities,
    quest branching, or endings) are not yet documented in official sources.
  </p>

  <h2>Controls overview</h2>
  <p>
    The official description lists the following controls. See the
    <a href="/controls/">Controls page</a> for the full table.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Left Click</strong> — Attack</li>
    <li><strong>Q</strong> — Dash</li>
    <li><strong>F</strong> — Defense</li>
    <li><strong>B</strong> — Finish move</li>
    <li><strong>H</strong> — Breathing</li>
    <li><strong>U</strong> — Quest Indicators</li>
    <li><strong>ALT</strong> — Lock</li>
    <li><strong>SHIFT</strong> — Run</li>
    <li><strong>M</strong> — Menu</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What is not yet confirmed (requires hands-on testing)</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Starting area or tutorial steps</li>
    <li>How to unlock the slayer or demon route</li>
    <li>First quest or objective</li>
    <li>How breathing works as a mechanic (styles, upgrades, effects)</li>
    <li>Character creation or stat allocation</li>
    <li>How to earn or spend in-game currency</li>
    <li>Inventory or equipment system</li>
    <li>Multiplayer or co-op features (if any)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Official resources</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Official game page:
      <a href="https://www.roblox.com/games/79833666916700/Demon-Born" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
        roblox.com/games/79833666916700/Demon-Born
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      SoraExp Roblox group:
      <a href="https://groups.roblox.com/v1/groups/34709042" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
        groups.roblox.com/v1/groups/34709042
      </a>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Contribute</h2>
  <p>
    If you have verified official information or hands-on observations to share,
    use the <a href="/contact/">correction workflow</a>.
    All published gameplay facts require either an official source or documented hands-on testing.
  </p>
</ContentLayout>